Sterling told Sunday Times Magazine: 'My ambition is to have my own song from the Kop. Last season I loved the song for Luis Suarez — [Steven] Gerrard and [Philippe] Coutinho have good ones too.

'Of course, when the crowd’s with you, there’s nothing better.'

Sterling will be hoping to help Liverpool to a crucial Premier League victory against Newcastle United on Monday evening as Brendan Rodgers' side look to close the gap to fourth-place Manchester City.

